sh App\" you can use: https://cash.me/$Lifeprint\nWant to order a USB drive with four semesters worth of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":72,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CJYCEM2rARgBIhMIkePFjbjrkwMVVYmKBx28pBztSLSG_6vJuYjDmwHKAQQXoip6","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbXRaUHl6cGJZY2wwdTBuTUQ1MndUa2NSdmk1UXxBQ3Jtc0tsRGV1REJ4VVZuMXBfdk1fWndnTmVGOTFDeWZJb044c01tWjh2T1ZlRlVmUUtqZVhkWXdBek5UUGJ3OWlJeUFPU0VUZk1ZOTJWdE0zOTlMVDFWQWFUTnJka1dIZVBwRC1yV1JBUERtZWhOZEtNd2R0cw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=m4YhzJV_wzQ","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbXRaUHl6cGJZY2wwdTBuTUQ1MndUa2NSdmk1UXxBQ3Jtc0tsRGV1REJ4VVZuMXBfdk1fWndnTmVGOTFDeWZJb044c01tWjh2T1ZlRlVmUUtqZVhkWXdBek5UUGJ3OWlJeUFPU0VUZk1ZOTJWdE0zOTlMVDFWQWFUTnJka1dIZVBwRC1yV1JBUERtZWhOZEtNd2R0cw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=m4YhzJV_wzQ","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":184,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CJYCEM2rARgBIhMIkePFjbjrkwMVVYmKBx28pBztSLSG_6vJuYjDmwHKAQQXoip6","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbW9kMEo0a1NISGQ5cUN3X0VmMVh4bEdqNlJQQXxBQ3Jtc0ttY3FJYlpiWEtZcGxiVzl5V19MeVVmeEFtQlFhU0FaejB6aWYxb0d1UXJ5Rnl6cUJ5X0pYbW1Sa3o5VWhQbGFsaEtXNGJ4Tk1EU1JEQlZDak1w